  <!--

  oiledmachine-overlay notes


  Build-time environment variables:

  COLLECTION_DB_PATH - Path to the vector database storing collections
  Default:  collections

  EMBEDDING_MODEL - The name of the embedding model used for the vector database
  Default:  granite-embedding-107m-multilingual

  FILE_ASSETS - Directory path to store and retrieve uploaded file assets
  Default:  assets

  LISTENING_ADDRESS - The port to connect to LocalRecall server
  Default: :8080

  OPENAI_BASE_URL - Base URL for the embedding model API
  Default:  http://localai:8080

  VECTOR_ENGINE - Vector database engine
  Default:  chromem

  See also https://github.com/mudler/LocalRecall/blob/v0.4.1/README.md#-environment-variables

  -->
  <upstream>
    <bugs-to>https://github.com/mudler/LocalRecall/issues</bugs-to>
